Dependency Information

Apache Maven

<dependency>
  <groupId>org.ensor.robots</groupId>
  <artifactId>snackbot</artifactId>
  <version>1.0-SNAPSHOT</version>
</dependency>

Apache Buildr

'org.ensor.robots:snackbot:jar:1.0-SNAPSHOT'

Apache Ant

<dependency org="org.ensor.robots" name="snackbot" rev="1.0-SNAPSHOT">
  <artifact name="snackbot" type="jar" />
</dependency>

Groovy Grape

@Grapes(
@Grab(group='org.ensor.robots', module='snackbot', version='1.0-SNAPSHOT')
)

Grails

compile 'org.ensor.robots:snackbot:1.0-SNAPSHOT'

Leiningen

[org.ensor.robots/snackbot "1.0-SNAPSHOT"]

SBT

libraryDependencies += "org.ensor.robots" %% "snackbot" % "1.0-SNAPSHOT"
